oai_dc:dc.dc:title: 2011: Close up look at the water levels of the 2011 Flood on a pylon
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: 2011 flood; water;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The pylon at the Mud Island boat docks after the flood. The horizontal lines mark the stopping points of the waters as they rose and fell. Some house boats are to the left and the marina gas station docks are on the right.
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Shaw, Lindsey
